  <data key="d1">instructor</data>
  <data key="d2">Jianer Chen is the instructor for CSCE 608, with contact details: email j-chen3@tamu.edu, office PETR 428, and phone (979) 845-4259.&lt;SEP&gt;The instructor for the course and author of the supplementary reading materials.&lt;SEP&gt;Jianer Chen is the instructor for CSCE 669.&lt;SEP&gt;Author of the required textbook "Introduction to Tractability and Approximability of Optimization Problems."</data>
