<node id="Midterm Exam">
  <data key="d0">Midterm Exam</data>
  <data key="d1">exam</data>
  <data key="d2">An exam scheduled for March 6 during Week 8.&lt;SEP&gt;A midterm exam is part of the course's grading, contributing 15% to the final grade. It is taken in-class.&lt;SEP&gt;Midterm Exam is an in-class examination.&lt;SEP&gt;One of the two exams contributing to the Exams Grade Component, worth 30% of the final grade, given in class.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e71d1b10edbe0c32853ef56c45777750&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa3afc12a670cd1cb0dbbd58a21ee6f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25f55d55aa02142a4fef3a59667d54e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfa1933458123176fbbd95a49ddd5dac</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
