<node id="Spring 2026">
  <data key="d0">Spring 2026</data>
  <data key="d1">academicterm</data>
  <data key="d2">Spring 2026 is an academic term or semester during which a variety of Computer Science and Engineering (CSCE) courses are offered. Specifically, it is the period when CSCE 608, CSCE 611, CSCE 612, CSCE 632, CSCE 633, CSCE 638, CSCE 665, and CSCE 669 are available. For CSCE 669, this academic semester runs from January 12, 2026, to May 5, 2026.&lt;SEP&gt;Spring 2026 is the semester during which the CSCE 670 course is offered, with a start date of January 12, 2026, and an end date of May 5, 2026.&lt;SEP&gt;The academic term during which CSCE 672 is offered.`</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a3e414e857408077610cba428e4c3c9c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4a3f0ae82d59413c6c528c03f0295f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a2b290b8c85fed51f1c2c7eb6d238c88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4bdb718cd78e7b20f7debd300686d75&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d02f5f686cd8436fd29bcb456fe407e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-077cc1807c0d82b343cfcef5d57ae46a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4af25c76d7c75c4d2b7b81f83f1bfed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2384cead57358b5db5cb910f416830cb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd928783cfa5ec68fdff2fbd6acd025c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2066e03585785691c0b7ccdffe6ae6f5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774773524</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="College Station">
  <data key="d0">College Station</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">College Station is identified as the primary location for the offering of multiple CSCE courses. Specifically, it is where CSCE 608, CSCE 611, CSCE 612, CSCE 629, CSCE 638, CSCE 641, and CSCE 656 are offered. These descriptions consistently refer to College Station as a general location, a geographical location, or a campus location for these course offerings. Additionally, College Station holds relevance not only for the course offerings but also for the instructor's office.&lt;SEP&gt;The campus location where CSCE 665 is offered.&lt;SEP&gt;The campus where the CSCE 669 course is held.&lt;SEP&gt;College Station is the location where the CSCE 670 course is offered.&lt;SEP&gt;The location where the CSCE 672 course is offered.`</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a3e414e857408077610cba428e4c3c9c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4a3f0ae82d59413c6c528c03f0295f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a2b290b8c85fed51f1c2c7eb6d238c88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8f161d98e4794412ee58f5d230dfb13&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4bdb718cd78e7b20f7debd300686d75&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-077cc1807c0d82b343cfcef5d57ae46a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5782089503e5bebb6b73d325a524565&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c282fe2bb2e5dc2027e6af44cb55ca3c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4af25c76d7c75c4d2b7b81f83f1bfed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2384cead57358b5db5cb910f416830cb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd928783cfa5ec68fdff2fbd6acd025c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2066e03585785691c0b7ccdffe6ae6f5</data>
