<node id="AI Statement">
  <data key="d0">AI Statement</data>
  <data key="d1">academicpolicy</data>
  <data key="d2">A policy regarding the strict prohibition of AI use in the course.&lt;SEP&gt;A policy that explicitly prohibits the use of AI, copilot, or LLMs and specifies that violations will be treated as cheating.&lt;SEP&gt;This policy explicitly prohibits the use of AI in the course.&lt;SEP&gt;A policy outlining the ethical and effective use of Artificial Intelligence tools in the course.&lt;SEP&gt;The AI Statement outlines the course policy on the use of Generative AI tools, emphasizing documentation, ethical conduct, and referring to Texas A&amp;M University Student Rule 20 regarding academic misconduct.&lt;SEP&gt;A policy outlining the rules regarding the use of AI tools in course work, specifically prohibiting them for review writing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fa3afc12a670cd1cb0dbbd58a21ee6f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed2e32490a3c719b08ed196b1bd6e19b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a863d6fab8e70ebbab93357f389a2a60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b1183a4902499625d751db4da1be964&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2cbc6507438dd741ecc6e529fe954278&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d188bffad2de46a2d40cc892e31ab869</data>
