<node id="Course Specific Attendance Policy">
  <data key="d0">Course Specific Attendance Policy</data>
  <data key="d1">academicpolicy</data>
  <data key="d2">A policy outlining recommendations for class attendance, responsibilities for missed material, and rules for making up missed exams.&lt;SEP&gt;This policy outlines student responsibilities for class attendance and participation, and details the conditions for make-up exams.&lt;SEP&gt;A policy outlining specific attendance requirements for the course, particularly for in-person sections.&lt;SEP&gt;This policy strongly recommends class attendance, outlines student responsibility for missed material, and details conditions for making up missed exams.</data>
