<node id="Instructor">
  <data key="d0">Instructor</data>
  <data key="d1">instructor</data>
  <data key="d2">The Instructor is a faculty or academic staff member primarily responsible for teaching a course. This individual plays a crucial role in managing the course's academic and administrative aspects.

Key responsibilities of the Instructor include handling unusual circumstances related to attendance and exams, and students are expected to consult with them regarding such matters, including excused absences and extensions. They are available for contact to address questions or special circumstances that students may encounter. Additionally, the Instructor may provide educational resources such as sample code on the course website to aid students.

Beyond direct instruction and student support, the Instructor holds several administrative duties. They are responsible for establishing and modifying grade multipliers and have the authority to assign failing grades. They also approve team project barriers and may receive mandatory interview notes, confirming interview details with relevant organizers.&lt;SEP&gt;The course instructor who may request meetings with students to assess their understanding of their code.&lt;SEP&gt;The person responsible for teaching the course and granting permission for late submissions.&lt;SEP&gt;The faculty member responsible for the course, who should be consulted about unusual circumstances in advance.&lt;SEP&gt;The person to discuss unusual circumstances with regarding late submissions.&lt;SEP&gt;A course staff member who can be contacted by students for clarification on homework problems.&lt;SEP&gt;The course instructor who assists students in making up missed work after absences.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fa3afc12a670cd1cb0dbbd58a21ee6f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-491622aa2feb07cb2cecb5393f78ed43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4645a5b8880a1c596bee106a995c6ffd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed2e32490a3c719b08ed196b1bd6e19b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e8805bcc946c2b61a1328f138f7fa9c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a863d6fab8e70ebbab93357f389a2a60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-49cbdcaf6f02cb17eb1de01b94ff2d2b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c1466d3818184682c27ba9ee5556dc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5f93f882082dd2e8bd9f6fea3705879&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8fd05ebe6b24797879aeca3e63cfcb39&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d053b26d12136a5abb64ba2275c1d35d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d188bffad2de46a2d40cc892e31ab869&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17117391581adcb92ff362fd7657041c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-007361532f5a9b6614541c85881c7ed9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-963f08e9468a8386b210c963f7d81dd4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ddfe50b5e19b936f6b3d27b70a9b0306</data>
