<node id="CSCE 611">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 611</data>
  <data key="d1">course</data>
  <data key="d2">CSCE 611 is an Operating Systems course, section 600 (50668), offered in Spring 2026 in College Station, with 3 credit hours, meeting on Tuesdays and Thursdays from 5:30 PM to 6:45 PM in EABB 106, from January 12, 2026, to May 5, 2026.</data>
