  <data key="d1">gradecomponent</data>
  <data key="d2">These are tasks that students must submit, subject to the Late Work Policy.&lt;SEP&gt;Assignments are tasks that students need to complete, which may require TAMU HPRC access and can be programmed in Python.&lt;SEP&gt;Assignments collectively account for 31% of the total grade. This component includes Assignment 0, Assignment 1, Assignment 2, and Assignment 3.&lt;SEP&gt;A component of the final grade, contributing 20%, requiring individual submission of tasks related to analyzing and visualizing data.</data>
