  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">CSCE 632 Accessible Computing explores disenfranchised user populations due to disability, ethical and legal motivations for accessible technology, universal design, and the application of accessibility standards in software and computer-based solutions.</data>
