<node id="Justify Ethical And Practical Need For Accessibility">
  <data key="d0">Justify Ethical And Practical Need For Accessibility</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Students will learn to justify the ethical and practical need for accessibility to employers and clients using evidence-based arguments and effective communication strategies.</data>
