<node id="Compare And Critique Models Of Disability">
  <data key="d0">Compare And Critique Models Of Disability</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Students will learn to compare and critique different models of disability, including the civil rights model, and analyze their impact on approaches to accessibility.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-88f4d8e2b60cb901518686edff30fd85</data>
