  <data key="d0">Assess Facilitators And Barriers To Technology Use</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Students will learn to assess facilitators and barriers to technology use, and design or recommend strategies that reduce barriers and support accessibility for diverse users.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-88f4d8e2b60cb901518686edff30fd85</data>
