  <data key="d0">Develop Accessible Technologies, Documents, And Presentations</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Students will learn to develop accessible technologies, documents, and presentations that comply with established standards, and evaluate their effectiveness for people with disabilities as well as other populations.</data>
