  <data key="d0">Critique Technology For Accessibility Standards</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Students will learn to critique technology, identifying instances where accessibility standards may be insufficient, and propose design alternatives that fulfill the underlying goals of accessibility.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-88f4d8e2b60cb901518686edff30fd85</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774772958</data>
