  <data key="d0">Design, Implement, And Evaluate Equitable Interaction Solutions</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Students will learn to design, implement, and evaluate solutions that enable equitable interaction, mediating challenges and barriers for specific disabilities, and justify design choices within the framework of universal design principles.</data>
