  <data key="d0">Creative Pursuits</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Creative pursuits, including writing, coding, and drawing, are considered critical to education, with AI technologies shaping how these tasks are approached, and require integrity, originality, and ethical conduct.</data>
