<node id="Evaluation">
  <data key="d0">Evaluation</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">Students are expected to describe how they evaluated Generative AI tools as part of their documentation.&lt;SEP&gt;Evaluation is a course topic discussed in Week 7.&lt;SEP&gt;Evaluation, in the context of web search and recommender systems, is a key concept covered in CSCE 670.</data>
