<node id="Machine Learning Course">
  <data key="d0">Machine Learning Course</data>
  <data key="d1">course</data>
  <data key="d2">A course detailing its grading policy, late work policies, module schedule, assignments, exams, and technical requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;This course focuses on evaluating mathematical relationships within advanced machine learning algorithms, understanding supervised and unsupervised learning paradigms, and designing, implementing, and applying various advanced machine learning algorithms in real-world applications.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ce19d80ec4482577c0c7dfdb40a6b6a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942343fa7db4b93679179e294760f458</data>
