<node id="CSCE 641">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 641</data>
  <data key="d1">course</data>
  <data key="d2">CSCE 641 is a Computer Graphics course offered in Spring 2026 at College Station, with 3 credit hours. It provides an in-depth introduction to physically based rendering.&lt;SEP&gt;A course focusing on the foundations of rendering and their application in practical image synthesis systems.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4e992a7f5e94e73cc019b56f1967758&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5782089503e5bebb6b73d325a524565</data>
