<node id="CSCE 641 Practical Image Synthesis Systems">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 641 Practical Image Synthesis Systems</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">Application of rendering theories in functional software and hardware setups to create images, covered in CSCE 641.&lt;SEP&gt;Systems used for generating images in practical applications, covered in CSCE 641.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4e992a7f5e94e73cc019b56f1967758&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5782089503e5bebb6b73d325a524565</data>
