  <data key="d1">prerequisite</data>
  <data key="d2">A course that serves as a prerequisite or corequisite for CSCE 641.&lt;SEP&gt;A prerequisite course required for enrollment in CSCE 641.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4e992a7f5e94e73cc019b56f1967758&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5782089503e5bebb6b73d325a524565</data>
