  <data key="d0">Instructor Approval</data>
  <data key="d1">prerequisite</data>
  <data key="d2">An alternative requirement for CSCE 641 if course prerequisites are not met.&lt;SEP&gt;A prerequisite for the course, requiring permission from the course instructor.&lt;SEP&gt;A prerequisite for the VIZA 676 / CSCE 679 course, requiring students to obtain approval from the instructor.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4e992a7f5e94e73cc019b56f1967758&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73e30e4c7c97a587d29fb1fb52580342&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09a6a201103757a8631c43eea5625d97</data>
