<node id="CSCE 641 Understand Principles Outcome">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 641 Understand Principles Outcome</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Upon completion of CSCE 641, learners will understand physical and mathematical principles underlying light transport, image formation, and physically based rendering, including radiometric quantities and the rendering equation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4e992a7f5e94e73cc019b56f1967758</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774773142</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="CSCE 641 Implement Algorithms Outcome">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 641 Implement Algorithms Outcome</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Upon completion of CSCE 641, learners will be able to implement core rendering algorithms such as ray tracing, direct illumination, and global illumination methods.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4e992a7f5e94e73cc019b56f1967758</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774773142</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="CSCE 641 Analyze Monte Carlo Algorithms Outcome">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 641 Analyze Monte Carlo Algorithms Outcome</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Upon completion of CSCE 641, learners will be able to analyze sources of bias and variance in Monte Carlo rendering algorithms and evaluate the impact of different sampling and acceleration strategies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4e992a7f5e94e73cc019b56f1967758</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774773142</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="CSCE 641 Design Physically Based Rendering System Outcome">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 641 Design Physically Based Rendering System Outcome</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Upon completion of CSCE 641, learners will be able to design and implement a physically based rendering system or component that integrates multiple techniques covered in the course.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4e992a7f5e94e73cc019b56f1967758</data>
