  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">A fundamental concept in CSCE 641, related to the physical and mathematical principles of how images are created.&lt;SEP&gt;The mathematical formulation and practical solutions for how images are created, covered in CSCE 641.</data>
