  <data key="d0">CSCE 641 Physically Based Rendering</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">An in-depth introduction to rendering techniques that accurately model the physical behavior of light, with an emphasis on Monte Carlo techniques.&lt;SEP&gt;A key rendering approach covered in CSCE 641, simulating the physics of light.</data>
