  <data key="d0">CSCE 656 Computers and New Media</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">This course topic investigates the potential and realized impact of computers in the design of new media, explores relationships between authors and readers of interactive materials, and the influence of media design and content expressed.</data>
