  <data key="d0">CSCE 670</data>
  <data key="d1">course</data>
  <data key="d2">CSCE 670 is a course on Information Storage and Retrieval offered in Spring 2026 at College Station, with Section 600 (46627). It carries 3 credit hours.&lt;SEP&gt;This course covers various topics related to information retrieval, recommender systems, and large language models, structured across 15 weeks with assignments, quizzes, and a group project.</data>
