<node id="Course Grading Policy">
  <data key="d0">Course Grading Policy</data>
  <data key="d1">academicpolicy</data>
  <data key="d2">The Course Grading Policy defines the grading scale for the course: A (&gt;=90%), B (&gt;=80% and &lt;90%), C (&gt;=70% and &lt;80%), D (&gt;=60% and &lt;70%), F (&lt;60%).</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4375e28268d2a8a30d4105aa2942d3a6</data>
