<node id="Group Project Grade Component">
  <data key="d0">Group Project Grade Component</data>
  <data key="d1">gradecomponent</data>
  <data key="d2">The Group Project comprises 20% of the final grade, requiring students to work in teams of 3 or 4 on a mini-research project.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4375e28268d2a8a30d4105aa2942d3a6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774773457</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Homework Collaboration Policy">
  <data key="d0">Homework Collaboration Policy</data>
  <data key="d1">academicpolicy</data>
  <data key="d2">A policy for homework assignments emphasizing individual code writing, encouraging discussion of approaches and methods, and prohibiting pair programming, code sharing, or working through specific code problems together. It also requires acknowledging all help.&lt;SEP&gt;The Homework Collaboration Policy states that homeworks are individual assignments.&lt;SEP&gt;Students are permitted to talk to any other class member or work in groups to discuss homework assignments.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4375e28268d2a8a30d4105aa2942d3a6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ebdd535fdf10cab1c91d762a5888f4e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-226a3d7b35279fb5024bf203866c977e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774773599</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Jupyter Notebook">
  <data key="d0">Jupyter Notebook</data>
