  <data key="d0">Individual Semester-Long Project</data>
  <data key="d1">assignment</data>
  <data key="d2">A significant data mining project undertaken by students over the course of the semester, composed of five major deliverables.&lt;SEP&gt;A major course component consisting of five deliverables: Data Selection, Initial Research Question, Deep Dive, Project Showcase, and Final Deliverable.&lt;SEP&gt;The individual semester-long project contributes 40% to the overall grade.</data>
