  <data key="d1">academicpolicy</data>
  <data key="d2">The course grade scale defines the letter grade thresholds: A &gt;= 90, B &gt;= 80 and &lt; 90, C &gt;= 70 and &lt; 80, D &gt;= 60 and &lt; 70, F &lt; 60.</data>
