<edge source="Late Work Policy" target="Student Rule 7">
  <data key="d7">14.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation known as (Late Work Policy, Student Rule 7) defines the connection between the Late Work Policy and Student Rule 7. This relation indicates that the Late Work Policy is informed by, refers to, and references Student Rule 7. Specifically, the Late Work Policy clarifies and references Student Rule 7 concerning excused absences, particularly regarding the provision and exemption of makeup work for such absences. Student Rule 7 serves as the foundational basis for how the Late Work Policy addresses situations involving excused absences and their corresponding makeup work requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;The general Late Work Policy references Student Rule 7 for exemptions regarding makeup work for excused absences.&lt;SEP&gt;The Late Work Policy refers to Student Rule 7 regarding excused absences.&lt;SEP&gt;The Late Work Policy references Student Rule 7 regarding excused absences.&lt;SEP&gt;The Late Work Policy refers to Student Rule 7 for exemptions related to excused absences and makeup work.&lt;SEP&gt;The Late Work Policy is associated with Student Rule 7.&lt;SEP&gt;The Late Work Policy refers to Student Rule 7 as the basis for exemptions.</data>
  <data key="d9">basis,basis for,clarifies,compliance,exemption,governed by,legal basis,policy basis,policy details,policy exemption,reference,references</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e71d1b10edbe0c32853ef56c45777750&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d11c13929103dfefb983be96841e8dd8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c53b1e368af6bad831cd9b96486285d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfa1933458123176fbbd95a49ddd5dac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-49cbdcaf6f02cb17eb1de01b94ff2d2b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-381218105af92b28f283452a63c63ea1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01bc4d956199eea04809225050dec80b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24d121840ef425d19d7f4be65a994242&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d188bffad2de46a2d40cc892e31ab869&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-007361532f5a9b6614541c85881c7ed9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ebdd535fdf10cab1c91d762a5888f4e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-073f3905d25e07b3de0c6af600fbb64b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-963f08e9468a8386b210c963f7d81dd4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4084eda47ece732e28955a2801108cb1</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1774773691</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Late Work Policy" target="Course Specific Late Work Policy">
  <data key="d7">9.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Course Specific Late Work Policy is a specialized policy that represents a particular instance or type of a broader, general Late Work Policy. Its primary function is to provide specific details and rules that modify, specify, or expand upon the guidelines set forth in the general policy.

This course-specific version offers a more detailed framework for late submissions, often introducing additional or stricter regulations tailored for a particular course. It serves to elaborate on and, in some cases, enforce more stringent requirements beyond what is established in the overarching Late Work Policy.&lt;SEP&gt;The Course Specific Late Work Policy provides specific details for the general Late Work Policy.</data>
  <data key="d9">detail,details,extends,is a type of,modifies,overrides,policy type,specialization,specialized policy,specification,specifies,supplements,type of</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e71d1b10edbe0c32853ef56c45777750&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d11c13929103dfefb983be96841e8dd8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c53b1e368af6bad831cd9b96486285d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfa1933458123176fbbd95a49ddd5dac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-49cbdcaf6f02cb17eb1de01b94ff2d2b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01bc4d956199eea04809225050dec80b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ebdd535fdf10cab1c91d762a5888f4e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-073f3905d25e07b3de0c6af600fbb64b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4084eda47ece732e28955a2801108cb1</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1774773691</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
